No-Show Recorded for Your Adoption Appointment
============================================

Dear <%= @user.name %>,

We noticed that you did not arrive for your scheduled adoption pickup of <%= @pet&.name %> on <%= @adoption_date.strftime('%A, %B %-d, %Y') %>.

Pet Details:
- Name: <%= @pet&.name %>
- Type: <%= @pet&.pet_type&.capitalize %>
<% if @pet&.breed.present? %>- Breed: <%= @pet.breed %>
<% end %><% if @pet&.age.present? %>- Age: <%= @pet.age %> years
<% end %>

What Happens Next?
==================
You have the opportunity to reschedule your adoption. However, you're only allowed up to 2 reschedules. If you miss another appointment after that, your adoption request will be automatically rejected.

Our admin team will be in touch shortly with options to reschedule your adoption. If you have any questions or would like to reschedule right away, please contact us.

If you're unable to proceed with the adoption at this time, please let us know so we can make <%= @pet&.name %> available to other loving families.

